column2: SELECT A.RAJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,A.DEJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,        A.zphot,A.SFR_UV,A.logMstar,        C.ra,C.dec,C.objID,C.z,        D.class,D.subClass,        E.ssfr as ssfrFGED,E.logMass as logMassFGED,        F.ssfr as ssfrFGWD,F.logMass as logMassFGWD.        G.SFR as SFRMPP,G.logMass as logMassMPP	 FROM   MyDB.CCOSEDProps AS A   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(A.RAJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,A.DEJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,#/#.) AS B   JOIN SpecPhoto as C on B.objID=C.objID   JOIN SpecObj as D on C.specObjID=D.specObjID   LEFT JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyDust as E on C.specObjID=E.specObjID   LEFT JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as F on C.specObjID=F.specObjID   LEFT JOIN stellarMassPassivePort as G on C.specObjID=G.specObjID INTO    MyDB.CCOSEDProps_SpecPhotoFGED
